            <div class="h-100 p-5 bg-light rounded-3">
                <h2>Open source <i class="bi bi-balloon-heart"></i></h2>
                <p class="lead">Sa11y is 100% free and open source. You can view the <a href="https://github.com/ryersondmp/sa11y">source code on GitHub.</a> Sa11y was made open source in 2020 to help content authors around the world create accessible content for people with disabilities.</p>
                <p>Sa11y was originally developed as a custom accessibility checker for {{ site.university}}'s content management system and its several hundred content authors.</p>
            </div>
